  "body": "As discussed with @alcuadrado, the `verify-contract` task could verify the compiled bytecode against the deployed bytecode when publishing sources on Etherscan for improved reliability.\r\n\r\nThis can be achieved relying on the `eth_getCode` API to obtain the deployed bytecode and performing a linear search for matching local bytecode, thus getting rid of the `contractName` task parameter altogether.",
