    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I've done a quick analysis, it seems that the changes can be restricted to the `index.ts` file where:\r\n- the deployed bytecode can be retrieved using `eth_getCode` through Etherscan API\r\n- the local bytecode can be accessed using the `Artifact` returned by the `readArtifact` function\r\n\r\nThen a check can be added to raise a `BuidlerPluginError` if they don't match.\r\n\r\nGetting rid of the `contractName` parameter can be achieved by:\r\n- reading the compiler output from Buidler cache (i.e. add an internal task `TASK_GET_COMPILER_OUTPUT` and return compiler output from `TASK_COMPILE`)\r\n- performing a linear search matching the bytecode to extract the full contract name\r\n",
